                    "name": "Arcane Prepared Spells",
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "text": "DC 26, attack +18; <b>4th</b><i><u><a aonid=\"40\" game-obj=\"Spells\">clairvoyance</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"172\" game-obj=\"Spells\">lightning bolt</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"255\" game-obj=\"Spells\">resilient sphere</a></u></i>; <b>3rd</b><i><u><a aonid=\"119\" game-obj=\"Spells\">fireball</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"138\" game-obj=\"Spells\">glyph of warding</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"289\" game-obj=\"Spells\">slow</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"309\" game-obj=\"Spells\">stinking cloud</a></u></i>; <b>2nd</b><i><u><a aonid=\"2\" game-obj=\"Spells\">acid arrow</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"28\" game-obj=\"Spells\">blur</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"150\" game-obj=\"Spells\">hideous laughter</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"271\" game-obj=\"Spells\">see invisibility</a></u></i>; <b>1st</b><i><u><a aonid=\"110\" game-obj=\"Spells\">fear</a></u></i> (x2), <i><u><a aonid=\"122\" game-obj=\"Spells\">fleet step</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"189\" game-obj=\"Spells\">mending</a></u></i>; <b>Cantrips</b><b>(4th)</b><i><u><a aonid=\"3\" game-obj=\"Spells\">acid splash</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"61\" game-obj=\"Spells\">daze</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"66\" game-obj=\"Spells\">detect magic</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"171\" game-obj=\"Spells\">light</a></u></i>, <i><u><a aonid=\"246\" game-obj=\"Spells\">read aura</a></u></i><br/>",
                    "subtype": "offensive_action",
                    "offensive_action_type": "spells"
                },
                {
                    "name": "Breach the Abyss",
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "text": "<b>Requirements</b> The demonologist's last action was to cast a non-cantrip spell; <b>Effect</b> The demonologist siphons energy drawn from the Abyss into their weapon. Until the end of the turn, the weapon deals an extra 2d6 damage. Roll 1d20 to determine the type: 1-7 acid, 8-9 cold, 10-11 electricity, 12-18 fire, 19-20 negative.",
                    "subtype": "offensive_action",
                    "action": {
                        "type": "stat_block_section",
                        "subtype": "action",
                        "name": "Free Action",
                        "image": "FreeAction.png"
                    }
